                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120701-92-off549 t18120701-92-cd550"></join>, a pair of breeches, value 7 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120701-92-victim784" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
